description: Ancona, Italy In this video you will be on a glider and fly alongside the birds in Ancona, a seaport city in the Marche region, in central Italy. The flight takes off from a large field and you will see the church of San Francesco from above. The flight then moves on to the Adriatic Sea, where you will experience the breath-taking sea view. There is no audio in this video.
